creator: Mault Code
descriptionHtml:
DeadTD is a tower defense strategy game that allows the player to build and design a defense that is not limited by predefined locations. Towers can be used to block paths and group monsters up. Control the pace of the battle with the ability to pause anytime to build, sell, and upgrade towers. You can also increase the speed and rush the next wave if you are so bold! Each tower can be upgraded in power and eventually changed into a more specific type of tower. Every wave increases in difficulty, so you must stay vigilant or you will quickly die! If you really enjoyed a level, you can choose to play endless mode which only stops when you die or quit.

Currently, there is at least 20 different levels with over 30 different towers to build and upgrade.

This release is what is considered an alpha version and drastic changes can occur in future updates. Leaving comments, feedback, suggestions is very helpful in development!
descriptionShort: Build a tower defense to defeat the enemies before they reach the end of the map

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Support for older API version enabled once again.
More interface improvements
The tutorial is now part of the first and second levels
Added some new monster art

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Drones, User Interface Improvements, and Much More

New drones are now used to build and repair towers. They use energy to move around and must return to the command center to recharge. You can control the drones from the side panel drone tab.

Added some new monsters, including two that attack your towers!

Improved In-Game User Interface.

Lots of other changes, updates, and improvements!

title: Dead TD - Tower Defense Game

creator: Mault Code
descriptionHtml:
Dead TD is a tower defense game that was inspired by the old school original tower defense games. It features a wide range of towers that upgrade into more powerful types and features a range of different abilities that can be used to create the ultimate defense.

Build and Block using Towers! Create a maze or redirect monsters to group them up!

Pick from 8 Base Towers! Each tower having 3 possible upgrade paths!

Level up a hero, with 3 different classes, each with a variety of skills!

Battle against a variety of monsters including flying, stealth, immune, and attacking!
descriptionShort: Build a tower defense to defeat the enemies before they reach the end of the map
